    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ……\nダメ、これくらいじゃまだまだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff*\nNo‚ that’s not good enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nもう一度曲を流して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nPlease start the music again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.235854848225912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もう二時間ぶっ通しだぞ\n休憩した方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been at this non-stop for two hours straight.\nYou should take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな悠長なことは言ってられません\n撮影まであと三日しかないんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There isn’t much time left.\nThe shoot is in three days.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "それまでに、もっと、はぁ、体を\nはぁ、はぁ、しぼら、ないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to… *huff* get myself…\n*huff* *huff* slimmed up… before then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ。完全に息が上がってるじゃないか\n明らかにオーバーワークだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. You’re completely out of breath.\nYou’re clearly overextending yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "でも……撮影が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… the shoot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん、焦ってないか？　君らしくないな\n頼むから休憩をとってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san‚ it’s not like you to get so anxious.\nTake a break. Please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……実は、このお話をいただいてから\n水着グラビアについて勉強したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did some research into swimsuit gravure\nafter accepting this offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "水着グラビアの勉強？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Research? Into swimsuit gravure?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "実は私、こういうの恥ずかしくて\n見ないというか……避けてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve always avoided this sort of thing\nbecause I was embarrassed about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "コンビニに行っても男性向け雑誌の\nコーナーにはなるべく近づかないよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I even avoid the men’s magazine section\nwhen I go to a convenience store.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、女の子には目の毒かもしれないし\n天動さんがそうするのも理解は出来るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not exactly appealing to a lot of girls.\nI fully understand why you wouldn’t want to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "でもお仕事をいただいた以上\n水着グラビアについて知らない訳にはいきません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ having accepted the offer‚\nI needed to know more about swimsuit gravure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "だから意を決して\n男性向けコーナーに行ってみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I made up my mind\nand went to the men’s magazine section.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　いや、ちょっと待ってくれ\n同じ水着グラビアでも、そっち系じゃ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Wait a second.\nEven though they’re both about swimsuits‚ the style is completely diff—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "そして……\n完全に敗北しました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And…\nI was utterly defeated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え？　何に負けたんだ？\nそもそも勝負じゃないんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What are you defeated by?\nThis isn’t a competition…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "私と同世代の女の子達が、その……\nあんな姿で堂々と……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Girls around my age…\nLooking so confident in their revealing outfits…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "私、あんな風に自信を持って自分の水着姿を\n見せられません。水着グラビアを舐めてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn’t imagine wearing a swimsuit with such confidence.\nI underestimated swimsuit models.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "だから、あと三日以内に自信が持てるような\n体にならないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I need to gain a figure\nthat I can be confident about in three days…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いやいやいや！　天動さんが載る雑誌は女性誌だよ\n男性誌とはコンセプトが違うから、今のままでいいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a second‚ Tendo-san! It’s a women’s magazine that you’ll be appearing in.\nThey have a different concept from men’s magazines. You’re fine the way you are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも今回の撮影は星見プロに移籍して\n初めての単独の仕事です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this is my first solo job\nsince I moved to Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "だから絶対に星見プロに迷惑はかけたくありません\n完璧に撮影をこなせるよう、準備を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t let Hoshimi Productions down.\nI need to do everything I can to prepare‚ and make this absolutely perfec—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは嬉しいけど、天動さん\nそれは違う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I appreciate the sentiment‚ Tendo-san\nbut you’ve misunderstood something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "プロダクションのためにアイドルがいるんじゃない\nアイドルのためにプロダクションがあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols don’t exist for the sake of their agency.\nIt’s the other way around—agencies exist to serve idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
