      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "だから星見プロのために、なんて考えなくていい\n自分自身のために仕事に取り組んでほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t think about what you can do for Hoshimi Productions.\nThink about doing it for yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それが結果的には、ファンを一番喜ばせる\n俺はそう考えている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think ultimately that’s what\nthe fans really want to see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
