      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "……そんな風に考えたこと\n今までありませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’ve never thought about\nthings that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロでは、アイドル達本人がどう思うかよりも\n事務所としての方針が優先されてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At Van Productions‚ the agency’s strategy always came first‚\nno matter what the idol thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロのやり方を否定する気はない\nでも、俺はアイドルの自主性を尊重したいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t intend to criticize Van Productions’ policy.\nMy policy‚ however‚ is to respect each idol’s independence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "朝倉さんや姫野さんが聞いたら\n青いって笑われるかもしれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess Asakura-san and Himeno-san\nwill laugh at me for being naive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 218.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
