      "text": "新人のサニピと月ストをここまで育て上げたのは\n{user}さんじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You took Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest\nfrom humble beginnings to where they are today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
