      "text": "手始めに今回の仕事を完璧にこなします\n次はポージングの練習です。チェックお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first step would be to do a perfect job here.\nNext up is posing practice. Could you check for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.76666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
